
# Use Nmap to query SSL Cert details and filter the output to display cert name and expiry 

nmap --script=ssl-cert.nse -p 443 [NETWORK].1-255 | grep 'report\|ssl-cert\|after'

Nmap scan report for [hostname] ([IP Address])
| ssl-cert: Subject: commonName=*.[domain]/organizationName=[Organisation]/countryName=AU
| Not valid after:  2020-09-30T12:00:00

